title: Blessed Indeed
itunes:title: Blessed Indeed
description:
Sometimes the reason we’re not seeing bigger blessings is because we’re asking too small. If you want to see the uncommon, you have to pray for the uncommon. Don’t limit what God can do in your life. Dare to believe for unprecedented blessings!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
